data.description: Discover serene living in this beautifully remodeled ranch-style home, nestled in a peaceful tree lined neighborhood surrounded by a cove. Remodeled down to the studs in 2019, this residence offers modern comforts while retaining its rustic charm. Step inside to find a spacious living area, where a grand wood burning fireplace and mantel create a warm focal point, perfect for cozy gatherings. Listen to the rain serenading the metal roof as you relax in this inviting haven. The back section of the home was added new in 2019. Extra large bedrooms make this home feel like a custom build. Lake access through the community park (.2 of a mile away) lets you enjoy boating and fishing on the constant-level lake, while majestic oak trees provide shade over the property, making the side/backyard a perfect retreat. Sitting on 1.5 lots there is plenty of room to spread out! A 20x16 shed was added in 2021 providing ample storage space, and a separate 8x10 she-shed with electricity (finished out and currently used as an office) was also added in2021. This versatile space can be used as a craft room, workshop, or pool house. Imagine the possibilities – the large shed has 9ft ceilings so could be combined for a charming tiny home escape or ADU. Bring all your water toys and your RV! There is RV parking and an electric hook-up available. Swimspa added in 2022 is negotiable. Recent home updates include freshly painted interiors, new windows, and meticulous farmhouse window trim. All-new doors, modern bathroom fixtures, and a host of thoughtful touches showcase the attention to detail. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home where modern luxury, natural beauty, and rustic elegance blend seamlessly. Experience a lifestyle of tranquility and convenience – make this extraordinary property yours today. Minutes to restaurants and shopping in Kingsland or 10 miles to Marble Falls.
